    {
      "id": "59336e7baff09e000096b108",
      "text": "POLOLU-2459",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496542844,
      "updated": 1496542881
    },
    {
      "id": "59336ebcaff09e000096b10f",
      "text": "[フォトリフレクタ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496542909,
      "updated": 1496542914
    },
    {
      "id": "59336ea2aff09e000096b10d",
      "text": "デジタル出力が出るのでADCがないRasPiでも読めるが、GPIOの電圧でON/OFFを見るのではなく、outputにしてHIを出力した後、readしつづけてLOに戻るまでの時間を測るって使い方をする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496542883,
      "updated": 1496545465
    },
    {
      "id": "59336ebbaff09e000096b10e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496542907,
      "updated": 1496542907
    },
    {
      "id": "59336e7baff09e000096b109",
      "text": " Set the I/O line to an output and drive it high.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496542844,
      "updated": 1496542847
    },
    {
      "id": "59336e7baff09e000096b10a",
      "text": " Allow at least 10 μs for the sensor output to rise.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496542844,
      "updated": 1496542847
    },
    {
      "id": "59336e7baff09e000096b10b",
      "text": " Make the I/O line an input (high impedance).",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496542844,
      "updated": 1496542847
    },
    {
      "id": "59336e7a18c4750011223ed4",
      "text": " Measure the time for the voltage to decay by waiting for the I/O line to go low.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496542844,
      "updated": 1496542847
    },
    {
      "id": "59336e7faff09e000096b10c",
      "text": "[Pololu - QTR-1RC Reflectance Sensor (2-Pack) https://www.pololu.com/product/2459]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496542848,
      "updated": 1496542864
    },
    {
      "id": "59337863aff09e000096b111",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496545379,
      "updated": 1496545379
    },
    {
      "id": "59337862aff09e000096b110",
      "text": "\tメーカーの出してるライブラリとセットでArduinoで使うなら良いかもしれない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496545379,
      "updated": 1496545404
    },
    {
      "id": "59337879aff09e000096b112",
      "text": "\t「デジタル出力だからADCのないRasPiでも使えるぞ！」とか思ったけど、めんどくさい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496545402,
      "updated": 1496545496
    },
    {
      "id": "59338478aff09e000096b115",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1496548472,
      "updated": 1496548472
    },
    {
